snippet.textDisplay:
I really hoped that all the tall tales with Flameheart were just a transition to 9 new tall tales on the same theme. I was really happy last year with the drastic turn you made with the tall tales, the arena, etc ... But now I'm very disapointed of what you offer us for this 2th anniversary (not talking about the recycled content) which is very weak.

You probably did what you could but all I see is reworked existing stuff and artificially increasing playing content, that's too much for me.

I'm not mentionning the upcoming release on Steam and all of us that can't migrate from this shitty Xbox app on PC to Steam.

Note that i've been supporting you guys since the very begining of the beta.

Anyway, keep up the work but I won't come back this time, maybe for the next tall tale for sure ! I wish you all good winds !


Also, sorry for potate english, i'm from the glorious french empire that don't like spanishempire (who knows, knows)
